NFS para sincronizar pastas dos nÃ³s
Origem:
apt install nfs-server
echo "/var/lib/docker/volumes/ 192.168.15.32(rw,sync,subtree_check) 192.168.15.33(rw,sync,subtree_check)" >> /etc/exports
exportfs -ar
showmount -e

Destino:
apt install nfs-common
mount -o v3 192.168.15.31:/var/lib/docker/volumes/ /var/lib/docker/volumes/


Docker Swarm
Master:
sudo docker swarm init --advertise-addr 192.168.15.31
Workers:
sudo docker swarm join --token SWMTKN-1-39zkhhg55spnccwru278lu4llp8wmraokh2fshruyd0n9dgdsf-b209qdl2thncq7al3jq8jj66k 192.168.15.31:2377
